    "Consider a scenario where the goal is to identify high-risk events from social media data.",
    "Users may first need an overview from different perspectives, such as the distribution of keywords over time or changes in sentiment for risk analysis.",
    "If outliers are identified, users may need further details, such as spatial distribution or entity relationships.",
